                            <comment id="12764312" author="fizx" created="Sat, 10 Oct 2009 08:12:58 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch below, as Jira file upload is not working for me:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;src/java/org/apache/solr/handler/XMLLoader.java #70&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replace&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;throw (IOException) new IOException(e.getMessage()).initCause(e); &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;throw new SolrException(SolrException.ErrorCode.BAD_REQUEST, e.getMessage(), e);&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
